channel.title: Compiling Error (Client)
channel.description:
I'm getting a Compile error on my server.
Note: Some input files use or override a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. Press any key to continue.
I've Google searched before making this topic and I don't see anyone with my problem, it may be similar but it's not my problem. My error doesn't even compile it doesn't do anything except for just tell me this. What can I do?

item.title: Compiling Error (Client)
item.dc:creator: @Deus1993 Deus1993
item.description:
@Deus1993 wrote:

That’s not an error, that just means your java files are using deprecated things (stuff that is no longer used)

Everything still compiled fine.
